{"type": "article", "id": 24166, "title": "毛毡墙角垫", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-21T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142124zOJq6aTpP8BjkILd.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">墙面的转角如果没有柜子或其他装饰来填充总会显得有一些空，瑞典设计师 Ola Giertz 就用方形的羊毛毡设计了一个墙饰，可以用不同的形状或色块搭配，让墙面变得活泼。当两个略有弯曲的羊毛毡拼在一起时，能形成一个小的隔断，放在办公室里是一个增加互动的地方。此外这种材料有隔音和减少回声的作用。<a href=\"http://www.olagiertz.se/ido.php\">这里是设计师的主页。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142122clUJTgsapO2HY6Ef.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142123aqjRk8INCXHseO6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142123K8cgoZdIpLUz4sr7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}